metadata.name: Begin Again
metadata.description:
Lost dreams often haunt our waking life. We feel lost &  abandoned, like a baby who still wishes to cling to their mother's warm bosoms. The promise of what could have been? 

Kill your darlings, move forward. So long as you live, there's hope to find new dreams. 
--------------------------------------------------------------

An Oil painting on Canvas
